Classic Monogram 4th Of July Wedding Invitation

Review Classic Monogram 4th Of July Wedding Invitation – 4th Of July Invitations Popular Classic Monogram 4th Of July Wedding Invitation It’s a great choice Classic Monogram 4th Of July Wedding Invitation See more about itThe focal point of this design is a simple monogram crest decorated with 2 USA flags. The design also features a "Greek Key" border and pattern backer. I’ve set the template up for a wedding invitation but all of the text fields are customizable to your needs. You can move, delete or add text fields by entering the design tool. You can also change the contrast color of the Greek Key border on the front and the pattern on the back (shown here as a dark blue) to any color you like by entering the design tool (underneath the text customization area, click to "customize further") then changing the background color on each side. Price:$2.09
